{"tid":2258641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨因應美國對台軍售 宣佈對洛歇馬丁、波音防務及雷神等實施制裁","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T08:16:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c4336021ec0e0e6494cf1a16beb82a7d8f75e533","tid":2258641,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"北京因應美對台新軍售 對有關美企及個人實施制裁<br />\n<br />\n北京因應美國對台新一筆軍售，宣布對洛歇馬丁、波音防務及雷神等美國企業，及在售台武器中發揮惡劣作用的美國個人與實體實施制裁，以維護國家利益。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府上星期宣布對台灣出售3款武器，總值約18億美元，當中包括SLAM-ER增程型防區外空對地導彈、&ldquo;海馬斯&rdquo;多管火箭炮及F-16戰機新型偵察吊艙。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2363298&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=5237b111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363298</a>"},{"pid":"902a895116153d5b0ee1c13e369ed134eb6a3e4e","tid":2258641,"uid":78470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:03:45.000Z","msg":"幾時制裁蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fc6d760fbc96a2cda129c8570396216b34d58f","tid":2258641,"uid":156913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"雷神...<br />\nHKAA點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89a0f4f4fe3b1193b391747d9ba5df1341456f9","tid":2258641,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"比啲骨氣 全中國包括香港唔好用雷神空管"},{"pid":"f519e9ddb6246c821731ca51cf097108637ba660","tid":2258641,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:06:10.000Z","msg":"毒撚宣佈制裁女神<br />\n方法:唔再stalk女神 唔再日日ig留言騷擾女神"},{"pid":"75cc544420f595b90c375d8f1713919006dd9e6a","tid":2258641,"uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht